        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"thumbs up\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f44d\" role=\"img\" title=\"thumbs up\">:thumbs_up:</span> cfallin submitted <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13224#pullrequestreview-4192567392\">PR review</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Generally looks great -- thanks for documenting all of this!</p>\n<p>(I didn't check the exact correspondence of where you added the <code># Errors</code> subsections to which functions should have then but I spot-checked, and trust that you carefully lined those up)</p>\n<p>Only a few thoughts on the table below...</p>\n</blockquote>",
